descriptionHtml:
This is a CME save of Mina~ Hope you like her!
This is for ECE users, she is made from the ygnord race.
The outfit in the image is what you have to look for yourself of course, but if you want to know it's Osare Culort Outfit - UNP


Required:

ENHANCED CHARACTER EDIT 1.4

If you want the character to look exactly like I have in the pictures you need these mods:
